4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will acquire skills in Windows and Linux administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence, while learning risk management and compliance with international standards. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The course content is available in English and Spanish. 

For more information, visit: [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop